/etc/environment

sudo gedit /etc/environment

must restart computer to enable the changes!

export 命令
locate 命令
sudo updatedb 更新locate索引 防止找不到文件

出现shared library 异常时 要注意
编译时 加入 $LD_LIBRARY_PATH  (缺失的 .so 文件的位置)
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/lib

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib/jvm/java-7-oracle/jre/lib/i386/client

export HADOOP_HOME=/home/victor/hadoop-1.0.3/hadoop-1.0.3
